Watch the most emotional moments between the Raney family and the homesteaders they help, from a sweet connection with a veteran whose equine therapy program was impacted by hurricane-force winds, to a tearful reveal for a single mom struggling to keep her family afloat.

Stream Homestead Rescue on discovery+ ► https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/homestead-rescue

About Homestead Rescue:
Marty, Matt and Misty Raney use their building, farming and hunting expertise to help people who strive to live off the grid.
